description: Overhanging branches cast moving shadows on the trail, swaying in the breeze like jagged arms reaching down from above to grasp unwary visitors.  Patches of ferns, deep green in the filtered moonlight, encroach on the path from both sides, their lacy fronds trampled into the soil here and there by passing hunters or prey.

title: [Yegharren Plain, Wooded Trail]
